text.div:
SilTHTerminology

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

https://terms.sil-th.org/ImplementationGuide/sil-th-terminology

A terminology registry which an be cited by FHIR artifacts

resource.name: ชุดรหัสอาชีพ ISCO-08
resource.description: ชุดรหัสอาชีพ ตามระบบ ISCO-08 The International Standard Classification of Occupations 2008 (ISCO-08) is a four-level hierarchically structured classification that covers all jobs in the world. Developed with the benefit of accumulated national and international experience as well as the help of experts from many countries and agencies, ISCO-08 is fully supported by the international community as an accepted standard for international labour statistics.
